Name: Average time from Awaiting Assignment to Batch to Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Total time it takes Awaiting Assignment to Batch to be followed by First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' and activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Minimum time between Awaiting Assignment to Batch and the subsequent Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Average cycle time of Awaiting Assignment to Batch across all variants ending with Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Total duration of Awaiting Assignment to Batch in variants that include SW-Reviewer Agreed earlier in the process
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' and the end of case where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs

Name: Average time from SW-Reviewer Agreed to Awaiting Assignment to Batch in cases where both activities occur
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Minimum elapsed time between SW-EIC Accept and Awaiting Assignment to Batch
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-EIC Accept' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Total time from Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation to Awaiting Assignment to Batch in revision-to-publication pathways
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Average time it takes Awaiting Assignment to Batch to occur after First Look-Your updates are overdue
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'First Look-Your updates are overdue' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Cycle time of Awaiting Assignment to Batch compared to the cycle time of Manuscript Export Succeeded in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Total waiting time to Awaiting Assignment to Batch following First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Minimum time from Awaiting Assignment to Batch to the final Manuscript Export Succeeded in accepted manuscript variants
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Average duration between SW-Reviewer Agreed (in any round) and Awaiting Assignment to Batch when the manuscript is eventually accepted
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Elapsed time between RW-EIC Accept and Awaiting Assignment to Batch in revised manuscript trajectories
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'RW-EIC Accept' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Time from the last occurrence of SW–Major Revision due in 1 week to Awaiting Assignment to Batch in multi-revision cases
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': activity == 'SW–Major Revision due in 1 week'", 'end': "activity == 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'", 'aggregation': 'average'}"
